FBIS4-10519 "drlat072_a_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-072 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba PRENSA LATINA Director Interviews Kim Il-Song PRENSA LATINA Director Interviews Kim Il-Song FL1404012994 Havana Tele Rebelde and Cuba Vision Networks in Spanish 0000 GMT 14 Apr 94 FL1404012994 Havana Tele Rebelde and Cuba Vision Networks Spanish BFN [Text] DPRK leader Kim Il-song has sent the Cuban people a message of solidarity. The statesman received Pedro Margolles, director of the Latin American news agency PRENSA LATINA, at Government Palace in Pyongyang. On that occasion, Kim Il-Song took advantage of the interview on the situation in the peninsula and throughout the world to send greetings to the Cubans and their president, Fidel Castro.
